{"title_page": "Arentim e Cunha", "text_new": "{{Infobox Portuguese subdivision\n|type = parish\n|official_name = Arentim e Cunha\n|image_shield = \n|region             = Norte\n|CIM                = [[C\u00e1vado (intermunicipal community)|C\u00e1vado]]\n|district           = [[Braga District|Braga]]\n|municipality       = [[Braga]]\n|area_total = 5.72\n|population_total = 1530\n|population_as_of = 2011\n|coordinates = {{coord|41.492|-8.509|type:adm1st_region:PT_dim:50000|display=inline,title}}\n|website = \n|footnotes =\n}}\n'''Arentim e Cunha''' is a [[Freguesia (Portugal)|civil parish]] in the municipality of [[Braga]], Portugal. It was formed in 2013 by the merger of the former parishes Arentim and Cunha.<ref>{{cite web|title=Law nr. 11-A/2013, pages 552 26-28|url=http://dre.pt/pdf1sdip/2013/01/01901/0000200147.pdf |accessdate=18 July 2014|author=''[[Di\u00e1rio da Rep\u00fablica]]''|language=Portuguese|format=pdf}}</ref> The population in 2011 was 1,530,<ref name=ine>[http://www.ine.pt/ngt_server/attachfileu.jsp?look_parentBoui=165404348&att_display=n&att_download=y Instituto Nacional de Estat\u00edstica (INE)], Census 2011 results according to the 2013 administrative division of Portugal</ref> in an area of 5.72&nbsp;km\u00b2.<ref name=dgt>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dgterritorio.pt/cartografia_e_geodesia/cartografia/carta_administrativa_oficial_de_portugal_caop_/caop__download_/carta_administrativa_oficial_de_portugal___versao_2017__em_vigor_/ |title=\u00c1reas das freguesias, concelhos, distritos e pa\u00eds |access-date=2018-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181105172426/http://www.dgterritorio.pt/cartografia_e_geodesia/cartografia/carta_administrativa_oficial_de_portugal_caop_/caop__download_/carta_administrativa_oficial_de_portugal___versao_2017__em_vigor_/ |archive-date=2018-11-05 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n[[Image:Arentim.jpg|thumb|left|Arentim Church]]\n[[Image:Cunha Church.jpg|thumb|left|Cunha Church]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n